name: The Kiss
description: Spectacular NFT ART. Nothing superfluous, elegant graphics, simple lines and silhouettes! The minimalism of this work does not let the eye get tired, while the black and white solution of the graphics gives the subject versatility.  The poster will fit perfectly, for example, both in a strict office design and in an airy bedroom. Print the file and mount it in a beautiful frame. The maximum print size is 23.4 x 16.5 inches / 40 x 60 cm (A2 format). Jpeg, 4961 x 3508 Pixels, 0,9 MB.
